data.description: Come see this charming 4 bed 2 bath corner home that has been tastefully remodeled. Kitchen has been completely re-done. Lots of front and back yard space! Solar panels have been completely paid off and are included in the sale! Owner also willing to leave any furniture! This is the perfect starter home for any family, or even the perfect investment opportunity. Close to shopping and freeway. Don't wait on this one too long!
